<i>noun</i>: 휴양지 [휴양지], 휴양소 [휴양소] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>휴양지 [휴양지]</dt><br>
<dd>resort; getaway; holiday destination</dd><br>
<dd>편안히 쉬면서 건강을 잘 돌보기에 알맞은 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>A place suitable for taking care of one's health by relaxing.</dd><br>
<dt>휴양소 [휴양소]</dt><br>
<dd>resort; recreation center</dd><br>
<dd>편안히 쉬면서 건강을 잘 돌볼 수 있도록 시설을 갖추어 놓은 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>A place equipped with facilities for taking care of one's health by relaxing.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>